            </div>
                                <h4 class="fancy-heading-panel"><b>Body Parameters</b></h4>
        <div style=" padding-left: 28px;  clear: unset;">
            <b style="line-height: 2;"><code>username</code></b>&nbsp;&nbsp;
<small>string</small>&nbsp;
 &nbsp;
