                <h1 id="lab-maintenance">Lab Maintenance</h1>

    <p>Endpoints for managing lab maintenance blocks, holidays, and closures.</p>

                                <h2 id="lab-maintenance-POSTapi-admin-lab-maintenance-bulk-create">Bulk create maintenance blocks, holidays, or closures</h2>

<p>
<small class="badge badge-darkred">requires authentication</small>
</p>

<p>Creates multiple blocks across selected dates and time slots for a lab space.
Lab supervisors can only manage blocks for their assigned labs.</p>

<span id="example-requests-POSTapi-admin-lab-maintenance-bulk-create">
<blockquote>Example request:</blockquote>


<div class="bash-example">
    <pre><code class="language-bash">curl --request POST \
    "http://localhost:8000/api/admin/lab-maintenance/bulk-create" \
    --header "Authorization: Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_KEY}" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json" \
    --data "{
    \"lab_space_id\": 16,
    \"block_type\": \"architecto\",
    \"dates\": [
        \"architecto\"
    ],
    \"slots\": [
        \"architecto\"
    ],
    \"reason\": \"architecto\"
}"
</code></pre></div>


<div class="javascript-example">
    <pre><code class="language-javascript">const url = new URL(
    "http://localhost:8000/api/admin/lab-maintenance/bulk-create"
);

