                                <h2 id="registrations-POSTapi-events--event_id--register">Create Registration (RSVP)</h2>

<p>
<small class="badge badge-darkred">requires authentication</small>
</p>

<p>Registers the authenticated user for a specific event with a chosen ticket type.
Returns the registration details including QR code token for check-in.</p>

<span id="example-requests-POSTapi-events--event_id--register">
<blockquote>Example request:</blockquote>


<div class="bash-example">
    <pre><code class="language-bash">curl --request POST \
    "http://localhost:8000/api/events/1/register" \
    --header "Authorization: Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_KEY}" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json" \
    --data "{
    \"ticket_id\": 1,
    \"additional_data\": {
        \"t_shirt_size\": \"L\"
    }
}"
</code></pre></div>


